cdata.name: Dnotes
cdata.desc:
First launched in February 2014, DNotes is a blockchain-based digital currency and paymentsystem developed byDNotes Global Inc. It allows users to perform crypto transactions within the platform. In addition, DNotes features a vault service namedDNotes Vaultas well as anews and information media outlet, theDCEBrief.

The NOTE token is a Scrypt-based algorithm cryptocurrency. It is open source, uses a Proof ofStake (PoS) mechanism to reward, and charge a0.005 NOTE fee for eachtransaction made with the token.
